    <text xml:id="Site_WFY_Section_Bb_Cave41">
        <body>
            <div type="cave" xml:lang="zh">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="bold">41</hi>號窟</head>
                <div>
                    <head>概述</head>
                    <div>
                        <head>位置</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>該窟位於南坡<foreign xml:lang="en">B</foreign>區。</item>
                            <item>
                                <foreign xml:lang="en">f</foreign>壁方向：340°。</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>形制</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>疑為方形窟。</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>尺寸</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>窟底高於現在的小徑約2.5米。</item>
                            <item>窟口前部寬度為230釐米。</item>
                            <item>窟底進深：160釐米。</item>
                            <item>高度：168釐米。</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>保存狀況</head>
                        <p>石窟未完工。石窟的開鑿可能由窟底開始，然後從邊上向內鑿。窟頂尚未鑿出，因而尚留有石塊。</p>
                        <figure rend="page" n="figure" xml:id="Cave_41_DSC_0121.JPG">
                            <head xml:lang="zh">未完成的<hi rend="bold">41</hi>號窟；2010年拍攝</head>
                            <head>Unfinished cave <hi rend="bold">41</hi>; 
                            photograph taken in 2010</head>
                            <graphic url="Cave_41_DSC_0121.JPG"/>
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="cave" xml:lang="en">
                <head type="cave">Cave <hi rend="bold">41</hi>
                </head>
                <div>
                    <head>Description</head>
                    <div>
                        <head>Location</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>Southern slope, section B </item>
                            <item>Direction: wall f 340˚</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>Shape</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>Intended box shape</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>Measurements</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>Height above present walkway: ca. 2.5 meters</item>
                            <item>Width of opening at front 230 cm</item>
                            <item>Depth of floor: 160 cm</item>
                            <item>Height: 168 cm</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>State of preservation</head>
                        <p>Unfinished cave. The carving probably started from the floor and continued inwards from the sides.
                        The ceiling was not hollowed out; therefore, a block of stone is left at the centre.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </body>
